items.title: Some Social Security recipients to receive 2 monthly benefit checks in December
items.description: SSI recipients will receive two Social Security payments in December 2025 due to a calendar scheduling quirk that moves January's payment to Dec. 31.

items.title: Musk says AI and robotics are 'only' things that can solve massive US debt crisis
items.description: Elon Musk claims AI and robotics are the only solution to America's $38 trillion debt crisis, predicting dramatic economic changes within three years.
